text:
If COVID-19 immunity isn’t long lasting (latest research)
... then Aus should aim for bordered elimination (suppression is a slow fail)
... then NSW should lock down now? (40% reduction in cases for every _day_ earlier & lowest overall economic cost)

What’s wrong w my logic? 🤷🏼‍♂️
